## 🖥️ Server Details

| Site        | Server Name | IP Address   | Role      |
| ----------- | ----------- | ------------ | --------- |
| Delhi       | DEL-DHCP01  | 10.10.0.10   | Primary   |
| Mumbai      | MUM-DHCP01  | 172.168.0.10 | Secondary |
| Uttarakhand | UKD-DHCP01  | 192.168.0.10 | Secondary |

---

## ⚙️ Configuration Steps

---

### 🔧 STEP 1 – Install DHCP Role (Run on ALL Servers)

```powershell
Install-WindowsFeature -Name DHCP -IncludeManagementTools

# Authorize DHCP in Active Directory
Add-DhcpServerInDC -DnsName $env:COMPUTERNAME `
-IPAddress (Get-NetIPAddress -AddressFamily IPv4 | Where-Object {$_.InterfaceAlias -notlike "*Loopback*"}).IPAddress
```

---

### 🔧 STEP 2 – Create Delhi Scope (Run on DEL-DHCP01)

```powershell
Add-DhcpServerv4Scope `
-Name "Delhi-Scope" `
-StartRange 10.10.0.100 `
-EndRange 10.10.255.200 `
-SubnetMask 255.255.0.0 `
-State Active

Set-DhcpServerv4OptionValue `
-ScopeId 10.10.0.0 `
-Router 10.10.0.1 `
-DnsServer 10.10.0.5 `
-DnsDomain "cloud.local"
```

---

### 🔧 STEP 3 – Create Mumbai Scope

```powershell
Add-DhcpServerv4Scope `
-Name "Mumbai-Scope" `
-StartRange 172.168.0.100 `
-EndRange 172.168.255.200 `
-SubnetMask 255.255.0.0 `
-State Active

Set-DhcpServerv4OptionValue `
-ScopeId 172.168.0.0 `
-Router 172.168.0.1 `
-DnsServer 10.10.0.5 `
-DnsDomain "cloud.local"
```

---

### 🔧 STEP 4 – Create Uttarakhand Scope

```powershell
Add-DhcpServerv4Scope `
-Name "UKD-Scope" `
-StartRange 192.168.0.50 `
-EndRange 192.168.0.200 `
-SubnetMask 255.255.255.0 `
-State Active

Set-DhcpServerv4OptionValue `
-ScopeId 192.168.0.0 `
-Router 192.168.0.1 `
-DnsServer 10.10.0.5 `
-DnsDomain "cloud.local"
```

---

### 🔧 STEP 5 – Configure Failover (Delhi ↔ Mumbai)

```powershell
Add-DhcpServerv4Failover `
-Name "Delhi-Mumbai-FO" `
-PartnerServer "MUM-DHCP01.cloud.local" `
-ScopeId 172.168.0.0 `
-SharedSecret "P@ssw0rd123" `
-Mode HotStandby `
-ReservePercent 10 `
-MaxClientLeadTime 01:00:00 `
-AutoStateTransition $true `
-StateSwitchInterval 00:30:00
```

---

### 🔧 STEP 6 – Configure Failover (Delhi ↔ Uttarakhand)

```powershell
Add-DhcpServerv4Failover `
-Name "Delhi-UKD-FO" `
-PartnerServer "UKD-DHCP01.cloud.local" `
-ScopeId 192.168.0.0 `
-SharedSecret "P@ssw0rd123" `
-Mode HotStandby `
-ReservePercent 10 `
-MaxClientLeadTime 01:00:00 `
-AutoStateTransition $true `
-StateSwitchInterval 00:30:00
```

